text: haey puokke( puok mou sh ri ki n) minban leukatamkeung a l laoh aoy samnung than pitabrakd robsa trong laey khn del phendei teangmoul sthet knong kandabdai robsa trong now thngai barlok . haey mekh cheachraen chean ku trauv ban mour daoy daisdam robsa trong . trong mha saatasam ning khpangkhpasa ampi avei del puokke kampoung thveu shi ri k
